<div class="note-source" id="TSJN-01-03-0431-sn"><p><abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ recipient's copy ]">RC</abbr> (<span class="ref-rep" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Yale University Library ]">CtY</span>); at head of text: 13 [i.e., dispatch No. 13]. 3d. Copy. An unnumbered duplicate of the same dispatch is in <span class="ref-rep" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Historical Society of Pennsylvania, Philadelphia ]">PHi</span>. Both versions are entirely in Mazzeis hand, attesting his agitation and haste in informing TJ of the unpleasant result of the conference with Franklin.</p></div>
